This folder contains modified versions of custom source.F90 files
----------

From KIT (Germany): (originals are in vendor folder)
a) source_gamma_meshtal1.F90
b) source_gamma_meshtal2.F90

Adapted from KIT
c) source_gamma_meshtal2_ergbins.F90

More information about each file:
a) Not used
b) Original was modified from 24 energy groups to 42 groups
c) Modifications to read in another line from the gammas file. This additional line contains the energy bin values, starting from 0.0, and increasing to maximum energy of interest.

------
To use one of these in a custom compile of MCNP/DAGMCNP, one can link to the files in the
Source/src folder like this:
ln -s *path to this folder*/source_gamma_meshtal2.F90 source.F90

(or you could copy the file to that folder, but it won't get updated when changes happen)

----

